headline: Comstock Celebrates Starbucks Opening at Loudoun Station
summary: RESTON, Va., December 04, 2025--Comstock Holding Companies, Inc. (Nasdaq: CHCI) ("Comstock"), a leading asset manager, developer, and operator of mixed-use and transit-oriented properties in the Washington, D.C. region, announced today that Starbucks has opened its new 1,800-square-foot location at 22114 Gramercy Park Drive in Ashburn, Virginia, next to the lobby of BLVD Flats in Loudoun Station.
